<div class="BCL-concept">
<h2 id="faq">FAQs</h2>

<ol><li><strong>Can a Gallery site with a custom domain and SSL be only accessible via HTTPS?</strong> Yes, in fact this is the only way we allow the site to be accessed. If you try to access a site on the HTTP link, you will automatically be redirected to the HTTPS site. This is done by forcing HTTPS redirects in CloudFront.</li>
</ol></div>
